WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.185 align:middle line:90%


00:00:01.185 --> 00:00:02.810 align:middle line:84%
>>WILLIAM HENRY: Have
you ever wondered

00:00:02.810 --> 00:00:06.490 align:middle line:84%
what the human body was
really designed to do

00:00:06.490 --> 00:00:10.480 align:middle line:84%
or is capable of
doing spiritually?

00:00:10.480 --> 00:00:12.580 align:middle line:84%
>>CLARE HENRY: On this
episode of "Arcanum,"

00:00:12.580 --> 00:00:16.010 align:middle line:84%
we investigate the human
rainbow body of light.

00:00:16.010 --> 00:00:18.962 align:middle line:90%


00:00:18.962 --> 00:00:21.914 align:middle line:90%
[THEME MUSIC]

00:00:21.914 --> 00:00:36.200 align:middle line:90%


00:00:36.200 --> 00:00:38.270 align:middle line:84%
>>WILLIAM: Our
exploration of arcanum

00:00:38.270 --> 00:00:41.820 align:middle line:84%
has seen the repetition
of three key symbols:

00:00:41.820 --> 00:00:47.250 align:middle line:84%
a stone, a rod or a staff,
and a cloak of light.

00:00:47.250 --> 00:00:50.240 align:middle line:84%
>>CLARE: The stone is
the Philosopher's Stone.

00:00:50.240 --> 00:00:54.040 align:middle line:84%
The rod is the caduceus
or staff of life.

00:00:54.040 --> 00:00:57.280 align:middle line:84%
The cloak is the
garment of light.

00:00:57.280 --> 00:00:59.140 align:middle line:84%
>>WILLIAM: In
Western civilization,

00:00:59.140 --> 00:01:03.500 align:middle line:84%
the quest for arcanum begins
with humanity's eviction

00:01:03.500 --> 00:01:06.460 align:middle line:84%
of Adam and Eve from
the Garden of Eden.

00:01:06.460 --> 00:01:11.465 align:middle line:84%
The Old Testament god Yahweh
made a gate at the east of Eden

00:01:11.465 --> 00:01:16.540 align:middle line:84%
and placed a flashing,
flaming sword in its center.

00:01:16.540 --> 00:01:21.040 align:middle line:84%
>>CLARE: Humans were forbidden
to cross through the gate.

00:01:21.040 --> 00:01:24.770 align:middle line:84%
>>WILLIAM: Next, the Bible says,
the Old Testament god Yahweh

00:01:24.770 --> 00:01:27.270 align:middle line:90%
made coats of skin for humanity.

00:01:27.270 --> 00:01:30.450 align:middle line:84%
And these are assumed
to be animal skins.

00:01:30.450 --> 00:01:34.620 align:middle line:84%
>>CLARE: However, in the
esoteric or mystical tradition,

00:01:34.620 --> 00:01:36.890 align:middle line:90%
the skin is human skin.

00:01:36.890 --> 00:01:40.780 align:middle line:84%
Mystics believe that Adam
and Eve were originally

00:01:40.780 --> 00:01:43.160 align:middle line:90%
beings of light.

00:01:43.160 --> 00:01:44.800 align:middle line:84%
>>WILLIAM: Rabbinical
tradition also

00:01:44.800 --> 00:01:49.690 align:middle line:84%
says that Adam and Eve were
covered with a cloud of glory,

00:01:49.690 --> 00:01:54.390 align:middle line:84%
meaning they glowed
rainbow rays.

00:01:54.390 --> 00:01:57.060 align:middle line:84%
>>CLARE: Adam's
garment is identical

00:01:57.060 --> 00:02:00.010 align:middle line:84%
to the celestial
robes of the righteous

00:02:00.010 --> 00:02:04.010 align:middle line:84%
in the Jewish and Christian
mystery tradition.

00:02:04.010 --> 00:02:08.080 align:middle line:84%
>>WILLIAM: It is described as
a shining garment or garment

00:02:08.080 --> 00:02:09.970 align:middle line:90%
of light.

00:02:09.970 --> 00:02:13.550 align:middle line:84%
>>CLARE: It was of extraordinary
brilliance and splendor.

00:02:13.550 --> 00:02:17.060 align:middle line:84%
And because of it,
Adam and Eve possessed

00:02:17.060 --> 00:02:19.150 align:middle line:90%
supernatural qualities.

00:02:19.150 --> 00:02:22.780 align:middle line:84%
>>WILLIAM: This glowing
rainbow body was taken away

00:02:22.780 --> 00:02:27.570 align:middle line:84%
from humanity, mystics say,
and our goal is to reclaim it.

00:02:27.570 --> 00:02:29.240 align:middle line:84%
>>CLARE: In the
Dead Sea Scrolls,

00:02:29.240 --> 00:02:32.450 align:middle line:84%
the Essenes proclaimed
the faithful were

00:02:32.450 --> 00:02:36.450 align:middle line:84%
to receive life everlasting
and a crown of glory

00:02:36.450 --> 00:02:40.640 align:middle line:84%
and a robe of honor
amid light perpetual.

00:02:40.640 --> 00:02:42.760 align:middle line:84%
>>WILLIAM: Is it
possible that Adam

00:02:42.760 --> 00:02:46.090 align:middle line:84%
and Eve's glorious
and glowing garment

00:02:46.090 --> 00:02:50.250 align:middle line:84%
is the original body of
light within all of us?

00:02:50.250 --> 00:02:53.000 align:middle line:84%
>>CLARE: In William's
feature investigation,

00:02:53.000 --> 00:02:56.640 align:middle line:84%
we will explore the mystical
teaching that tells us

00:02:56.640 --> 00:03:01.970 align:middle line:84%
that we are all in the process
of morphing into a higher form.

00:03:01.970 --> 00:03:04.680 align:middle line:84%
In one lifetime,
we can transform

00:03:04.680 --> 00:03:09.700 align:middle line:84%
or morph into what they call
the rainbow body of light.

00:03:09.700 --> 00:03:17.760 align:middle line:90%


00:03:17.760 --> 00:03:20.650 align:middle line:10%
>>WILLIAM: My
investigation or awareness

00:03:20.650 --> 00:03:24.320 align:middle line:10%
of the rainbow body of
light or cloak of light

00:03:24.320 --> 00:03:29.900 align:middle line:10%
began in 1999 with this enticing
drawing of the baptism of Jesus

00:03:29.900 --> 00:03:32.330 align:middle line:10%
from Winchester, England.

00:03:32.330 --> 00:03:35.590 align:middle line:10%
In the drawing or in the
scene, we see John the Baptist

00:03:35.590 --> 00:03:39.650 align:middle line:10%
attuning Jesus to the higher
vibration of the Holy Spirit,

00:03:39.650 --> 00:03:42.020 align:middle line:10%
and an angel is
standing by to give him

00:03:42.020 --> 00:03:45.030 align:middle line:10%
his new cloak or
garment of light.

00:03:45.030 --> 00:03:47.690 align:middle line:10%
When I first saw
this, I was transfixed

00:03:47.690 --> 00:03:51.970 align:middle line:10%
by this process, this
attunement, this imagery.

00:03:51.970 --> 00:03:56.470 align:middle line:10%
And it prompted me to do wonder,
what is this cloak of light

00:03:56.470 --> 00:03:57.900 align:middle line:10%
that Jesus is receiving?

00:03:57.900 --> 00:04:00.650 align:middle line:10%
We know it was referred
to as a miracle garment

00:04:00.650 --> 00:04:03.150 align:middle line:10%
because after he
put on this garment,

00:04:03.150 --> 00:04:05.690 align:middle line:10%
he was able to
perform the miracles.

00:04:05.690 --> 00:04:09.380 align:middle line:84%
Symbolic of putting on new
clothing, this garment of light

00:04:09.380 --> 00:04:14.640 align:middle line:84%
represents a seal or
a garment of light

00:04:14.640 --> 00:04:19.250 align:middle line:84%
that enabled Jesus to move into
this dimension in a new way.

00:04:19.250 --> 00:04:22.940 align:middle line:10%
Thus, later Easter
traditions of Whitsunday

00:04:22.940 --> 00:04:25.170 align:middle line:10%
became the later
Easter tradition

00:04:25.170 --> 00:04:27.330 align:middle line:10%
of giving and
getting new clothing.

00:04:27.330 --> 00:04:31.050 align:middle line:10%
This is why we dress up
our children in new clothes

00:04:31.050 --> 00:04:31.830 align:middle line:10%
at Easter time.

00:04:31.830 --> 00:04:36.350 align:middle line:10%
It symbolizes the acquisition
of this new garment of light.

00:04:36.350 --> 00:04:37.990 align:middle line:84%
And this is what
he demonstrated,

00:04:37.990 --> 00:04:40.010 align:middle line:84%
Jesus did, at the
transfiguration.

00:04:40.010 --> 00:04:42.670 align:middle line:84%
After receiving it, he
showed the disciples

00:04:42.670 --> 00:04:46.110 align:middle line:84%
what was possible with
this garment of light.

00:04:46.110 --> 00:04:48.890 align:middle line:84%
It's described as the robe of
light, the robe of sanctity,

00:04:48.890 --> 00:04:51.740 align:middle line:84%
the robe of glory, the shining
garment, the garment of light,

00:04:51.740 --> 00:04:54.990 align:middle line:84%
the beaming garment, and
the rainbow body of light.

00:04:54.990 --> 00:04:58.380 align:middle line:84%
The Greek word that
describes it is Exousia.

00:04:58.380 --> 00:05:01.210 align:middle line:84%
It means authority,
jurisdiction, liberty, power,

00:05:01.210 --> 00:05:04.910 align:middle line:84%
right to act, ability,
privilege, capacity,

00:05:04.910 --> 00:05:06.900 align:middle line:90%
and strength.

00:05:06.900 --> 00:05:08.850 align:middle line:84%
And the question that
emerged in my mind

00:05:08.850 --> 00:05:12.280 align:middle line:84%
was, well, where did John
the Baptist get the cloak?

00:05:12.280 --> 00:05:14.670 align:middle line:84%
And the answer is is
that John, it is claimed,

00:05:14.670 --> 00:05:18.630 align:middle line:84%
was the reincarnation of
Elijah, the prophet who was last

00:05:18.630 --> 00:05:21.700 align:middle line:84%
seen ascending into the
heavens in a whirlwind.

00:05:21.700 --> 00:05:25.660 align:middle line:84%
And as John is ascending in
this classically rendered icon

00:05:25.660 --> 00:05:28.310 align:middle line:84%
depicting the
ascension of Elijah,

00:05:28.310 --> 00:05:33.380 align:middle line:84%
he transmits this holy
garment to his priest, Elisha.

00:05:33.380 --> 00:05:37.050 align:middle line:84%
And then later, Elijah
incarnates as John the Baptist,

00:05:37.050 --> 00:05:39.890 align:middle line:84%
and he goes and
reclaims this garment.

00:05:39.890 --> 00:05:43.350 align:middle line:10%
So from these bits and pieces
that I started assembling,

00:05:43.350 --> 00:05:47.130 align:middle line:10%
I began to realize that
this garment symbolizes

00:05:47.130 --> 00:05:49.870 align:middle line:10%
a transmittable
teaching or perhaps

00:05:49.870 --> 00:05:55.010 align:middle line:10%
a vibration that enables us
to ascend into the heavens.

00:05:55.010 --> 00:05:57.690 align:middle line:10%
Now in the ancient world,
they called the ascension

00:05:57.690 --> 00:06:00.570 align:middle line:10%
into the heavens
via a whirlwind.

00:06:00.570 --> 00:06:02.490 align:middle line:10%
But today, I think
this is what we

00:06:02.490 --> 00:06:05.960 align:middle line:10%
call a stargate or a wormhole.

00:06:05.960 --> 00:06:09.170 align:middle line:84%
I began to put these pieces
together and recognizing

00:06:09.170 --> 00:06:12.410 align:middle line:84%
that if we're going to
ascend through a stargate

00:06:12.410 --> 00:06:14.410 align:middle line:84%
or a wormhole,
that we first must

00:06:14.410 --> 00:06:17.950 align:middle line:84%
put on this cloak
or garment of light.

00:06:17.950 --> 00:06:21.160 align:middle line:10%
And so I spent the time
from the early 2000s,

00:06:21.160 --> 00:06:23.760 align:middle line:10%
just pulling on
this golden thread

00:06:23.760 --> 00:06:26.150 align:middle line:10%
or string of this
garment, if you will,

00:06:26.150 --> 00:06:29.420 align:middle line:10%
following the story of
Elijah reincarnating

00:06:29.420 --> 00:06:33.780 align:middle line:10%
as John the Baptist, and seeing
how he reclaimed this garment

00:06:33.780 --> 00:06:36.190 align:middle line:10%
and was able to
utilize its power

00:06:36.190 --> 00:06:38.640 align:middle line:10%
and potential for
his own well-being,

00:06:38.640 --> 00:06:42.070 align:middle line:10%
and then ultimately how
he transmitted this cloak

00:06:42.070 --> 00:06:46.470 align:middle line:10%
or garment of light to his
cousin Jesus at the baptism,

00:06:46.470 --> 00:06:50.340 align:middle line:10%
enabling Jesus then to
fulfill his earthly mission.

00:06:50.340 --> 00:06:53.971 align:middle line:84%
And I was just astounded by
the potential and possibility

00:06:53.971 --> 00:06:54.470 align:middle line:90%
of this.

00:06:54.470 --> 00:06:56.400 align:middle line:84%
And I wondered,
how come this isn't

00:06:56.400 --> 00:06:58.390 align:middle line:90%
the basic Christian teaching?

00:06:58.390 --> 00:07:01.660 align:middle line:84%
Why isn't it a popular
teaching in Christianity?

00:07:01.660 --> 00:07:04.350 align:middle line:84%
Why isn't the church
set up to assist us

00:07:04.350 --> 00:07:08.410 align:middle line:84%
in manifesting this incredibly
powerful garment of light?

00:07:08.410 --> 00:07:11.010 align:middle line:84%
And as I continued pulling
on this golden thread,

00:07:11.010 --> 00:07:14.860 align:middle line:84%
I realized that ultimately,
this garment of light

00:07:14.860 --> 00:07:19.070 align:middle line:84%
was one of the key symbols
of the esoteric version

00:07:19.070 --> 00:07:20.410 align:middle line:90%
of Christianity.

00:07:20.410 --> 00:07:23.300 align:middle line:84%
And I began seeking
artwork that reflected

00:07:23.300 --> 00:07:26.100 align:middle line:84%
the utilization or-- not
just the acquisition,

00:07:26.100 --> 00:07:28.770 align:middle line:84%
but utilization of
this garment of light.

00:07:28.770 --> 00:07:31.880 align:middle line:10%
Here we're looking at Antonio
Campi's beautiful painting

00:07:31.880 --> 00:07:35.580 align:middle line:10%
in the Louvre, "The Mysteries
of the Passion of Christ."

00:07:35.580 --> 00:07:37.360 align:middle line:10%
In the center of
the painting, we

00:07:37.360 --> 00:07:41.060 align:middle line:10%
see a fairly traditional
image of the crucifixion:

00:07:41.060 --> 00:07:43.630 align:middle line:10%
Jesus with the two
thieves on either side,

00:07:43.630 --> 00:07:47.200 align:middle line:10%
Mary Magdalene, the
mother Mary, is present.

00:07:47.200 --> 00:07:49.580 align:middle line:84%
And then as we pan
around the painting,

00:07:49.580 --> 00:07:52.050 align:middle line:84%
we start to see the
mystical version

00:07:52.050 --> 00:07:54.470 align:middle line:84%
of the story or the mystical
attributes of this story

00:07:54.470 --> 00:07:55.340 align:middle line:90%
emerge.

00:07:55.340 --> 00:07:58.460 align:middle line:84%
We see the
resurrection of Jesus.

00:07:58.460 --> 00:08:00.720 align:middle line:84%
He is lit up like
a lightning bug.

00:08:00.720 --> 00:08:03.380 align:middle line:84%
He's actually resurrecting
from the tomb.

00:08:03.380 --> 00:08:07.870 align:middle line:84%
He's manifested his glory
body or resurrection body

00:08:07.870 --> 00:08:10.130 align:middle line:90%
as Christianity refers to it.

00:08:10.130 --> 00:08:14.240 align:middle line:84%
And then 40 days
after the resurrection

00:08:14.240 --> 00:08:16.750 align:middle line:84%
of his attainment
of this light body,

00:08:16.750 --> 00:08:20.100 align:middle line:84%
we are introduced then to
the idea of the ascension.

00:08:20.100 --> 00:08:23.230 align:middle line:84%
And this is what happens in the
upper right of the painting,

00:08:23.230 --> 00:08:28.030 align:middle line:84%
where now we see Jesus, having
attained his light body,

00:08:28.030 --> 00:08:31.050 align:middle line:84%
is seen above this
spiraling or corkscrewing

00:08:31.050 --> 00:08:33.840 align:middle line:84%
mountain with angels
on either side of it.

00:08:33.840 --> 00:08:40.059 align:middle line:84%
And he's ascending into this
apparent whirlwind or vortex.

00:08:40.059 --> 00:08:45.170 align:middle line:84%
And we see a trail of righteous
souls following along with him.

00:08:45.170 --> 00:08:47.800 align:middle line:10%
And we recognize that
in this ascension,

00:08:47.800 --> 00:08:51.370 align:middle line:10%
Jesus is no longer in
his flesh and blood form.

00:08:51.370 --> 00:08:54.620 align:middle line:10%
He's in a body of
light, and he is now

00:08:54.620 --> 00:08:57.090 align:middle line:10%
ascending into the heavens.

00:08:57.090 --> 00:09:00.590 align:middle line:10%
Now Antonio Campi does
some extraordinary things

00:09:00.590 --> 00:09:01.340 align:middle line:10%
in this painting.

00:09:01.340 --> 00:09:04.020 align:middle line:10%
And in the detail, we
see Jesus ascending

00:09:04.020 --> 00:09:06.590 align:middle line:10%
with all the other righteous
souls that are following him

00:09:06.590 --> 00:09:10.510 align:middle line:10%
along this path of
souls into the cosmos.

00:09:10.510 --> 00:09:12.590 align:middle line:10%
These are the
successful souls who

00:09:12.590 --> 00:09:14.240 align:middle line:10%
have followed this
path or teaching

00:09:14.240 --> 00:09:17.050 align:middle line:10%
and attained the vibration
of the body of light

00:09:17.050 --> 00:09:20.840 align:middle line:10%
and are now capable of following
Jesus through this gateway.

00:09:20.840 --> 00:09:23.870 align:middle line:84%
And I documented this in my
book, The Secret of Sion:

00:09:23.870 --> 00:09:26.130 align:middle line:84%
Jesus's Stargate,
the Beaming Garment,

00:09:26.130 --> 00:09:29.170 align:middle line:84%
and the Galactic Core
in Ascension Art.

00:09:29.170 --> 00:09:31.670 align:middle line:84%
And this was a huge
inspiration for me,

00:09:31.670 --> 00:09:34.330 align:middle line:84%
this recognition that
the garment of light

00:09:34.330 --> 00:09:38.480 align:middle line:84%
is the foundation of
esoteric Christian teaching.

00:09:38.480 --> 00:09:40.950 align:middle line:90%
It is arcanum.

00:09:40.950 --> 00:09:43.760 align:middle line:84%
And so I began
collecting as many images

00:09:43.760 --> 00:09:48.490 align:middle line:84%
as I could of Jesus
manifesting this body of light.

00:09:48.490 --> 00:09:52.490 align:middle line:84%
It's not typical, because
the typical crucifixion scene

00:09:52.490 --> 00:09:55.260 align:middle line:84%
shows a bloodied
and tortured Jesus.

00:09:55.260 --> 00:09:57.960 align:middle line:84%
He's supposed to be
here to suffer for us.

00:09:57.960 --> 00:10:01.020 align:middle line:84%
He died for our sins
in order to save us

00:10:01.020 --> 00:10:02.950 align:middle line:84%
in traditional
Christian teaching.

00:10:02.950 --> 00:10:06.780 align:middle line:84%
But in the esoteric side,
he came here, rather,

00:10:06.780 --> 00:10:11.690 align:middle line:84%
to show us the way for us to
attain our own light body.

00:10:11.690 --> 00:10:15.490 align:middle line:84%
And the key fact that I realized
that a lot of these artists

00:10:15.490 --> 00:10:17.540 align:middle line:84%
operated from--
their premise was

00:10:17.540 --> 00:10:21.090 align:middle line:84%
that by tuning in
to images of Jesus

00:10:21.090 --> 00:10:26.510 align:middle line:84%
manifesting the light body,
we feed our own light body.

00:10:26.510 --> 00:10:27.010 align:middle line:90%
So here.

00:10:27.010 --> 00:10:28.540 align:middle line:84%
Look at this
crucifixion scene where

00:10:28.540 --> 00:10:32.380 align:middle line:84%
Jesus is manifesting this
rainbow colored light that's

00:10:32.380 --> 00:10:37.070 align:middle line:84%
exploding from within his
body, demonstrating the way

00:10:37.070 --> 00:10:40.570 align:middle line:84%
to attain the rainbow body of
light or the resurrection body,

00:10:40.570 --> 00:10:41.900 align:middle line:90%
as it's called.

00:10:41.900 --> 00:10:44.125 align:middle line:84%
See the spray of
energy all around him

00:10:44.125 --> 00:10:45.750 align:middle line:84%
and how those
closest to him were

00:10:45.750 --> 00:10:49.720 align:middle line:84%
able to absorb that
frequency or that vibration.

00:10:49.720 --> 00:10:52.350 align:middle line:10%
And it is us, of course,
who are close to Jesus

00:10:52.350 --> 00:10:57.080 align:middle line:10%
as he's manifesting this
glory body at this moment.

00:10:57.080 --> 00:11:00.700 align:middle line:10%
Another favorite example is
the "Eisenheim Altarpiece"

00:11:00.700 --> 00:11:04.690 align:middle line:10%
by Matthias Grunewald, where
we see Jesus resurrecting

00:11:04.690 --> 00:11:07.990 align:middle line:10%
from the grave as this
brilliant light being,

00:11:07.990 --> 00:11:12.070 align:middle line:10%
manifesting a light
as bright as the sun.

00:11:12.070 --> 00:11:16.040 align:middle line:84%
And we see him with this
rainbow colored aura of energy

00:11:16.040 --> 00:11:19.090 align:middle line:90%
all around his light body.

00:11:19.090 --> 00:11:22.280 align:middle line:84%
To me, these are
far more inspiring,

00:11:22.280 --> 00:11:25.190 align:middle line:84%
and indeed instructive from
the soul's perspective,

00:11:25.190 --> 00:11:29.110 align:middle line:84%
than seeing the traditional
bloodied and tortured Jesus.

00:11:29.110 --> 00:11:31.950 align:middle line:84%
And it gave me a sense that
I was on the right path

00:11:31.950 --> 00:11:34.780 align:middle line:84%
here to keep following
this direction here.

00:11:34.780 --> 00:11:38.470 align:middle line:84%
Follow the light body Jesus
rather than the suffering

00:11:38.470 --> 00:11:42.510 align:middle line:84%
Jesus was the message that
I found in these paintings.

00:11:42.510 --> 00:11:44.950 align:middle line:84%
Soon it became
around the year 2006,

00:11:44.950 --> 00:11:47.380 align:middle line:84%
and I had a very
fortunate meeting.

00:11:47.380 --> 00:11:49.950 align:middle line:84%
You might call it a
synchronistic meeting.

00:11:49.950 --> 00:11:52.250 align:middle line:84%
I was at a conference
in California,

00:11:52.250 --> 00:11:55.290 align:middle line:84%
and a lovely couple came up and
introduced themselves to me.

00:11:55.290 --> 00:11:57.690 align:middle line:84%
They were both in their
mid 50s, and they told me

00:11:57.690 --> 00:12:00.720 align:middle line:84%
they both had PhDs from the
Harvard Divinity School.

00:12:00.720 --> 00:12:01.710 align:middle line:90%
They lived in India.

00:12:01.710 --> 00:12:07.030 align:middle line:84%
They worked with the Dalai
Lama, translating Tibetan texts.

00:12:07.030 --> 00:12:10.610 align:middle line:84%
Their specialty, they said,
was the rainbow body of light,

00:12:10.610 --> 00:12:12.820 align:middle line:84%
and they wondered if I'd
ever heard of it before.

00:12:12.820 --> 00:12:13.910 align:middle line:90%
And I hadn't.

00:12:13.910 --> 00:12:16.470 align:middle line:10%
And they gave me a
brief explanation

00:12:16.470 --> 00:12:19.780 align:middle line:10%
of the rainbow body, which I'd
like to share with you now.

00:12:19.780 --> 00:12:22.230 align:middle line:10%
Essentially, this
practice is called

00:12:22.230 --> 00:12:27.630 align:middle line:10%
Dzogchen or the great
perfection or mystic rapture.

00:12:27.630 --> 00:12:31.430 align:middle line:10%
And what the Tibetans teach
is that a teacher or yogi who

00:12:31.430 --> 00:12:34.360 align:middle line:10%
has acquired the highest
forms of accomplishment

00:12:34.360 --> 00:12:37.800 align:middle line:10%
can transform the subtle
aspects of the human body

00:12:37.800 --> 00:12:41.500 align:middle line:10%
into pure light or what
is called the rainbow body

00:12:41.500 --> 00:12:43.140 align:middle line:10%
or body of light.

00:12:43.140 --> 00:12:46.210 align:middle line:84%
The idea is is that
we can accelerate

00:12:46.210 --> 00:12:50.670 align:middle line:84%
the frequency of the human
body and spin it into a vortex,

00:12:50.670 --> 00:12:55.485 align:middle line:84%
dissolving the body into light,
leaving behind only hair, toe,

00:12:55.485 --> 00:12:59.970 align:middle line:84%
and fingernails, which have
no nerves to be transmuted.

00:12:59.970 --> 00:13:01.870 align:middle line:84%
And as this couple
is telling me this,

00:13:01.870 --> 00:13:04.580 align:middle line:84%
my imagination's
just going wild.

00:13:04.580 --> 00:13:09.040 align:middle line:84%
I'm thinking this is incredible,
to think that the human body is

00:13:09.040 --> 00:13:12.830 align:middle line:84%
designed to be spun into
this vortex of multicolored

00:13:12.830 --> 00:13:17.840 align:middle line:84%
or rainbow colored light that
can then travel the cosmos.

00:13:17.840 --> 00:13:21.410 align:middle line:84%
And this couple was
very deeply enthusiastic

00:13:21.410 --> 00:13:23.180 align:middle line:90%
about sharing this with me.

00:13:23.180 --> 00:13:25.320 align:middle line:84%
And the reason
why, they said, is

00:13:25.320 --> 00:13:28.180 align:middle line:84%
because they're experts
in the rainbow body.

00:13:28.180 --> 00:13:31.550 align:middle line:84%
They work with the
Tibetans, and they told me

00:13:31.550 --> 00:13:35.100 align:middle line:84%
that my work actually
answered for them

00:13:35.100 --> 00:13:38.850 align:middle line:84%
a question that
the Tibetans never

00:13:38.850 --> 00:13:42.490 align:middle line:84%
would answer for them, either
because the answer was secret,

00:13:42.490 --> 00:13:45.740 align:middle line:84%
they said, or because
perhaps the Tibetans didn't

00:13:45.740 --> 00:13:47.470 align:middle line:90%
know the answer to the question.

00:13:47.470 --> 00:13:50.610 align:middle line:84%
But my work in Egypt answered
this question for them,

00:13:50.610 --> 00:13:51.550 align:middle line:90%
they said.

00:13:51.550 --> 00:13:56.400 align:middle line:84%
The question was, once these
Lamas have perfected their body

00:13:56.400 --> 00:13:59.320 align:middle line:84%
and manifested the
rainbow body of light,

00:13:59.320 --> 00:14:01.160 align:middle line:84%
the Tibetans teach
that then they

00:14:01.160 --> 00:14:05.990 align:middle line:84%
are able to travel to any of
the other 12 star systems--

00:14:05.990 --> 00:14:08.720 align:middle line:84%
13 star systems,
including our own--

00:14:08.720 --> 00:14:11.730 align:middle line:84%
where this resurrection
or rainbow body

00:14:11.730 --> 00:14:13.120 align:middle line:90%
teaching is taught.

00:14:13.120 --> 00:14:17.620 align:middle line:84%
And what they always wondered
was how do they get there?

00:14:17.620 --> 00:14:21.590 align:middle line:84%
In other words, how do they
get from Sol, our star system,

00:14:21.590 --> 00:14:27.510 align:middle line:84%
to Sirius or the Pleiades
or Orion or Arcturus or any

00:14:27.510 --> 00:14:30.070 align:middle line:84%
of the other number
of star systems

00:14:30.070 --> 00:14:32.330 align:middle line:84%
that are repeatedly
mentioned in myth

00:14:32.330 --> 00:14:34.810 align:middle line:84%
and sacred tradition
the world over?

00:14:34.810 --> 00:14:38.609 align:middle line:84%
I mean, if we can get there
from here, how do we get there?

00:14:38.609 --> 00:14:40.150 align:middle line:84%
And then they said
they were watching

00:14:40.150 --> 00:14:44.450 align:middle line:84%
my presentation, my DVD
presentation "Star Walkers

00:14:44.450 --> 00:14:46.130 align:middle line:84%
and the Dimension
of the Blessed"

00:14:46.130 --> 00:14:48.480 align:middle line:84%
about the ancient
Egyptian star walkers,

00:14:48.480 --> 00:14:50.620 align:middle line:90%
and they got their answers.

00:14:50.620 --> 00:14:54.660 align:middle line:84%
What I had proposed is that, in
the ancient Egyptian tradition,

00:14:54.660 --> 00:14:57.770 align:middle line:84%
Osiris acquired in
his resurrection

00:14:57.770 --> 00:14:59.810 align:middle line:90%
a garment of light.

00:14:59.810 --> 00:15:03.140 align:middle line:84%
And what I had observed is
that when Osiris acquires

00:15:03.140 --> 00:15:05.400 align:middle line:84%
his garment of light,
he's very often

00:15:05.400 --> 00:15:09.440 align:middle line:84%
shown on the arc of the millions
of years, which to me looks

00:15:09.440 --> 00:15:13.550 align:middle line:84%
exactly like the way modern
science portrays a wormhole.

00:15:13.550 --> 00:15:16.910 align:middle line:84%
And I started down
this path of comparing

00:15:16.910 --> 00:15:18.930 align:middle line:84%
the ancient Egyptian
star gods who

00:15:18.930 --> 00:15:21.860 align:middle line:84%
we're assured are
transformed humans

00:15:21.860 --> 00:15:23.710 align:middle line:84%
who became celestial
beings, that

00:15:23.710 --> 00:15:26.700 align:middle line:84%
being the entire premise of
the ancient Egyptian religion,

00:15:26.700 --> 00:15:29.900 align:middle line:84%
that a human can become a star
being or a celestial being

00:15:29.900 --> 00:15:31.540 align:middle line:90%
and travel the stars.

00:15:31.540 --> 00:15:35.680 align:middle line:84%
As for example, as we see
here, the resurrected Osiris

00:15:35.680 --> 00:15:37.570 align:middle line:90%
is now called Orion.

00:15:37.570 --> 00:15:40.270 align:middle line:84%
And he sails aboard his
wormhole shaped ship

00:15:40.270 --> 00:15:43.020 align:middle line:84%
of eternity or arc of
the millions of years

00:15:43.020 --> 00:15:44.547 align:middle line:84%
towards the field
of the blessed,

00:15:44.547 --> 00:15:48.420 align:middle line:84%
via-- accessed via
the star fields

00:15:48.420 --> 00:15:52.170 align:middle line:84%
of Orion, which is the
place the Egyptians were

00:15:52.170 --> 00:15:54.650 align:middle line:90%
trying to aim their souls to.

00:15:54.650 --> 00:15:57.870 align:middle line:84%
And so the couple said their
eyes are just big as saucers

00:15:57.870 --> 00:15:59.820 align:middle line:84%
as they're watching
this because they're

00:15:59.820 --> 00:16:03.600 align:middle line:84%
going back and connecting the
dots with the Tibetans, who

00:16:03.600 --> 00:16:06.460 align:middle line:84%
said that they can travel
to other star systems.

00:16:06.460 --> 00:16:08.140 align:middle line:90%
How do they do it?

00:16:08.140 --> 00:16:10.930 align:middle line:84%
Via a wormhole,
this couple said.

00:16:10.930 --> 00:16:13.700 align:middle line:84%
My work answered that
question of how, once they

00:16:13.700 --> 00:16:15.650 align:middle line:84%
manifest the rainbow
body of light,

00:16:15.650 --> 00:16:17.730 align:middle line:90%
they can travel the stars.

00:16:17.730 --> 00:16:19.170 align:middle line:84%
Something else
that inspired them

00:16:19.170 --> 00:16:22.600 align:middle line:84%
was my imagery I provided
in another presentation

00:16:22.600 --> 00:16:26.130 align:middle line:84%
where I documented my
experience on a cruise ship

00:16:26.130 --> 00:16:27.520 align:middle line:90%
in Luxor, Egypt.

00:16:27.520 --> 00:16:31.530 align:middle line:84%
We were invited to watch a
whirling Dervish dancer, very

00:16:31.530 --> 00:16:35.700 align:middle line:84%
special, 800-year-old
mystic Islamic dance.

00:16:35.700 --> 00:16:38.340 align:middle line:84%
And what happens is the
Dervish dancer comes out,

00:16:38.340 --> 00:16:40.730 align:middle line:90%
and he starts spinning in place.

00:16:40.730 --> 00:16:44.960 align:middle line:84%
He's going into a meditative
trance as he's spinning.

00:16:44.960 --> 00:16:47.690 align:middle line:84%
And before I know it, he's
got this flying saucer

00:16:47.690 --> 00:16:49.020 align:middle line:90%
around his body.

00:16:49.020 --> 00:16:51.410 align:middle line:84%
He looked like Elijah
to me, going up

00:16:51.410 --> 00:16:55.030 align:middle line:84%
into that heavens in a whirlwind
in his merkaba vehicle.

00:16:55.030 --> 00:16:58.510 align:middle line:84%
And I'm blown away by this
800-year-old mystic Islamic

00:16:58.510 --> 00:17:01.960 align:middle line:84%
dancer-- or dance
as he's performing

00:17:01.960 --> 00:17:05.970 align:middle line:84%
this incredible story
about human transformation.

00:17:05.970 --> 00:17:07.420 align:middle line:10%
And he's wielding this.

00:17:07.420 --> 00:17:11.490 align:middle line:10%
And then all of a sudden,
he pulls out a second skirt

00:17:11.490 --> 00:17:12.760 align:middle line:10%
and starts spinning it.

00:17:12.760 --> 00:17:14.420 align:middle line:10%
And my jaw drops.

00:17:14.420 --> 00:17:16.349 align:middle line:90%
It's like, wait a minute.

00:17:16.349 --> 00:17:17.760 align:middle line:90%
That's a wormhole.

00:17:17.760 --> 00:17:20.740 align:middle line:84%
This mystic Islamic
dancers is showing us

00:17:20.740 --> 00:17:24.270 align:middle line:84%
that our human body is
capable of being transformed

00:17:24.270 --> 00:17:26.599 align:middle line:84%
into a wormhole, which
is my entire premise

00:17:26.599 --> 00:17:28.800 align:middle line:84%
in my presentations
I had just been given

00:17:28.800 --> 00:17:31.520 align:middle line:84%
the day before to my
tour group in Egypt.

00:17:31.520 --> 00:17:34.520 align:middle line:84%
And here it is, right
before my very eyes.

00:17:34.520 --> 00:17:37.570 align:middle line:84%
So here's the comparison
between our Islamic dancer,

00:17:37.570 --> 00:17:41.140 align:middle line:84%
our whirling Dervish or Sufi
dancer, beside a wormhole.

00:17:41.140 --> 00:17:47.530 align:middle line:84%
And it's clear that 800 years
ago, somebody in Cairo, Egypt

00:17:47.530 --> 00:17:50.180 align:middle line:84%
imagined our body
dissolving into light

00:17:50.180 --> 00:17:54.400 align:middle line:84%
or transforming into a wormhole,
as we see happening here.

00:17:54.400 --> 00:17:56.620 align:middle line:10%
And what happened at
the end of the dance

00:17:56.620 --> 00:18:00.460 align:middle line:10%
is that he collapses
his second skirt,

00:18:00.460 --> 00:18:03.700 align:middle line:10%
and he wraps it into a bundle.

00:18:03.700 --> 00:18:08.250 align:middle line:10%
And his assistant brings a
linen shroud out, if you will.

00:18:08.250 --> 00:18:11.600 align:middle line:84%
And they wrap the bundle,
and he feeds milk to it.

00:18:11.600 --> 00:18:13.040 align:middle line:90%
And I'm just blown away.

00:18:13.040 --> 00:18:16.220 align:middle line:84%
I'm thinking, OK, I
get the message here.

00:18:16.220 --> 00:18:20.170 align:middle line:84%
We're talking about how we
emerge on the earth plane

00:18:20.170 --> 00:18:21.030 align:middle line:90%
as a soul.

00:18:21.030 --> 00:18:22.580 align:middle line:90%
How did we get here?

00:18:22.580 --> 00:18:25.560 align:middle line:84%
Well, we came through a
portal, our mother's womb

00:18:25.560 --> 00:18:26.910 align:middle line:90%
in the birth canal.

00:18:26.910 --> 00:18:29.300 align:middle line:84%
But before that,
how did we get here?

00:18:29.300 --> 00:18:31.650 align:middle line:84%
Maybe we came here
via a wormhole.

00:18:31.650 --> 00:18:33.901 align:middle line:84%
That's what this dance
seemed to suggest to me.

00:18:33.901 --> 00:18:35.650 align:middle line:84%
And in fact, after he
completed his dance,

00:18:35.650 --> 00:18:36.650 align:middle line:90%
I went up to the dancer.

00:18:36.650 --> 00:18:39.130 align:middle line:84%
And I said, wow, I'm
just absolutely stunned

00:18:39.130 --> 00:18:40.337 align:middle line:90%
by your performance.

00:18:40.337 --> 00:18:42.420 align:middle line:84%
What were you trying to
convey through that dance?

00:18:42.420 --> 00:18:43.620 align:middle line:90%
What's the message?

00:18:43.620 --> 00:18:45.460 align:middle line:84%
And through a translator,
he said, well,

00:18:45.460 --> 00:18:48.480 align:middle line:84%
I was explaining the
unity of heaven and earth.

00:18:48.480 --> 00:18:52.690 align:middle line:84%
And I'm like, wow, why can't
I bring you back to Nashville

00:18:52.690 --> 00:18:55.240 align:middle line:84%
with me or take you up
to Boston to MIT or over

00:18:55.240 --> 00:18:58.160 align:middle line:84%
to Stanford where these high
energy physics types are trying

00:18:58.160 --> 00:18:59.850 align:middle line:90%
to break the wormhole code?

00:18:59.850 --> 00:19:02.290 align:middle line:84%
And you can show it
to us because it's

00:19:02.290 --> 00:19:04.290 align:middle line:90%
all within our body.

00:19:04.290 --> 00:19:06.810 align:middle line:90%
Our body is the stargate.

00:19:06.810 --> 00:19:09.240 align:middle line:10%
Our body is the wormhole.

00:19:09.240 --> 00:19:12.297 align:middle line:10%
And so after this meeting with
this couple at this conference,

00:19:12.297 --> 00:19:14.130 align:middle line:10%
I went home, and I
started hitting the books

00:19:14.130 --> 00:19:15.310 align:middle line:10%
and started hitting the
internet and saying,

00:19:15.310 --> 00:19:17.190 align:middle line:10%
OK, I gotta see what
I can figure out here.

00:19:17.190 --> 00:19:19.256 align:middle line:10%
I'm tremendously inspired.

00:19:19.256 --> 00:19:20.880 align:middle line:10%
In fact, this couple
started sending me

00:19:20.880 --> 00:19:23.850 align:middle line:10%
PhD dissertations about
the rainbow body of light.

00:19:23.850 --> 00:19:27.120 align:middle line:10%
So some of what I'm going to
share with you in this episode

00:19:27.120 --> 00:19:29.070 align:middle line:10%
today comes from
that research that I

00:19:29.070 --> 00:19:31.346 align:middle line:10%
started doing as a
result of that couple.

00:19:31.346 --> 00:19:32.970 align:middle line:10%
And I always like to
give them the most

00:19:32.970 --> 00:19:35.680 align:middle line:10%
heartfelt thanks
for changing my life

00:19:35.680 --> 00:19:38.640 align:middle line:10%
and tipping me off
to this reality here.

00:19:38.640 --> 00:19:41.110 align:middle line:10%
And one of the examples that
I found is this one here.

00:19:41.110 --> 00:19:43.700 align:middle line:10%
It's a thangka from
the 17th century where

00:19:43.700 --> 00:19:48.040 align:middle line:10%
we see a Lama in the rainbow
body from the top down.

00:19:48.040 --> 00:19:48.680 align:middle line:10%
And look.

00:19:48.680 --> 00:19:53.700 align:middle line:10%
He looks exactly like our
mystic Islamic dancer performing

00:19:53.700 --> 00:19:56.010 align:middle line:10%
the wormhole dance,
as I call it.

00:19:56.010 --> 00:19:59.920 align:middle line:84%
He's spinning in place with
the same multi-colored imagery

00:19:59.920 --> 00:20:02.740 align:middle line:90%
and the same spinning motion.

00:20:02.740 --> 00:20:05.000 align:middle line:84%
Now look what we see
here in the detail.

00:20:05.000 --> 00:20:08.060 align:middle line:84%
Look what's all over
this Lama's body.

00:20:08.060 --> 00:20:11.700 align:middle line:84%
It's nothing less than
the Chintamani symbol

00:20:11.700 --> 00:20:14.310 align:middle line:84%
that we have referenced
over and over again

00:20:14.310 --> 00:20:16.290 align:middle line:84%
in the "Arcanum"
series, the symbol

00:20:16.290 --> 00:20:20.000 align:middle line:84%
for the wish-fulfilling jewel,
which I believe ultimately

00:20:20.000 --> 00:20:24.290 align:middle line:84%
the Chintamani is the symbol for
the attainment of the rainbow

00:20:24.290 --> 00:20:25.510 align:middle line:90%
body of light.

00:20:25.510 --> 00:20:28.950 align:middle line:84%
That's the ultimate
wish we all have,

00:20:28.950 --> 00:20:32.440 align:middle line:84%
is to manifest our rainbow
body of light, our glory body,

00:20:32.440 --> 00:20:34.490 align:middle line:84%
our resurrection
body, whatever term

00:20:34.490 --> 00:20:36.650 align:middle line:84%
we feel most
comfortable for using.

00:20:36.650 --> 00:20:39.470 align:middle line:84%
It's all telling the
same story, and it's not

00:20:39.470 --> 00:20:41.890 align:middle line:84%
just the Tibetans
or the Egyptians

00:20:41.890 --> 00:20:46.240 align:middle line:84%
or the mystic Islamics that
have this story encoded

00:20:46.240 --> 00:20:47.610 align:middle line:90%
within their traditions.

00:20:47.610 --> 00:20:50.790 align:middle line:84%
It's actually all
over the world.

00:20:50.790 --> 00:20:54.310 align:middle line:84%
It's essentially a universal
or global teaching.

00:20:54.310 --> 00:20:58.320 align:middle line:84%
In fact, as noted, it
doesn't even come from Earth.

00:20:58.320 --> 00:21:02.990 align:middle line:84%
It's taught in 13 star
systems, including our own.

00:21:02.990 --> 00:21:05.430 align:middle line:84%
And as I'm pondering that
and meditating on this,

00:21:05.430 --> 00:21:09.640 align:middle line:84%
I'm thinking, wow, there must
be beings coming and going

00:21:09.640 --> 00:21:11.770 align:middle line:84%
through these star
gates and wormholes

00:21:11.770 --> 00:21:13.730 align:middle line:90%
from all of these star systems.

00:21:13.730 --> 00:21:16.040 align:middle line:84%
And in fact all of
us have the ability

00:21:16.040 --> 00:21:19.550 align:middle line:84%
to manifest this rainbow
body of light and travel

00:21:19.550 --> 00:21:22.000 align:middle line:84%
to these other star
systems and beyond.

00:21:22.000 --> 00:21:24.710 align:middle line:84%
Here's a really good example
of the rainbow body of light.

00:21:24.710 --> 00:21:26.770 align:middle line:90%
This is Padmasambhava.

00:21:26.770 --> 00:21:30.080 align:middle line:84%
In the eighth century, he
came from India to Tibet

00:21:30.080 --> 00:21:32.560 align:middle line:84%
to teach the rainbow
body of light.

00:21:32.560 --> 00:21:35.990 align:middle line:84%
And I love this imagery here
because we see the swirling

00:21:35.990 --> 00:21:38.850 align:middle line:84%
energy around him
that symbolizes

00:21:38.850 --> 00:21:40.840 align:middle line:90%
the rainbow body of light.

00:21:40.840 --> 00:21:42.580 align:middle line:90%
But look at it through my eyes.

00:21:42.580 --> 00:21:46.120 align:middle line:84%
What do we see on the
outer rim of his body

00:21:46.120 --> 00:21:48.950 align:middle line:90%
but a portal or a gateway?

00:21:48.950 --> 00:21:52.250 align:middle line:84%
And it made me feel like
I was on the right track

00:21:52.250 --> 00:21:55.740 align:middle line:84%
here in uniting the
rainbow body of light

00:21:55.740 --> 00:21:58.930 align:middle line:84%
with the star gate
or the wormhole.

