00:24:48.610 --> 00:24:51.410 align:middle line:10%
to as the rainbow body of light.

00:24:51.410 --> 00:24:54.300 align:middle line:10%
It's all the same thing.

00:24:54.300 --> 00:24:57.490 align:middle line:84%
And by weaving my thread
through these traditions,

00:24:57.490 --> 00:25:00.300 align:middle line:84%
I've been able to put
together a more, perhaps,

00:25:00.300 --> 00:25:04.310 align:middle line:84%
comprehensive body of work
about the rainbow body

00:25:04.310 --> 00:25:07.320 align:middle line:84%
than you'll find in Christianity
or the Tibetan tradition

00:25:07.320 --> 00:25:08.870 align:middle line:90%
or the ancient Egyptian.

00:25:08.870 --> 00:25:13.160 align:middle line:84%
I believe we have to unite
all these traditions in order

00:25:13.160 --> 00:25:16.370 align:middle line:84%
