body of light is

00:25:33.700 --> 00:25:38.950 align:middle line:84%
in fact an energy field produced
by the body, specifically

00:25:38.950 --> 00:25:41.970 align:middle line:84%
manifesting from
the heart chakra.

00:25:41.970 --> 00:25:44.410 align:middle line:84%
And it may well be
that the divine spark

00:25:44.410 --> 00:25:47.810 align:middle line:84%
that the Gnostics referred
to is located in the heart,

00:25:47.810 --> 00:25:51.490 align:middle line:84%
and it is the source of the
manifestation of the rainbow

00:25:51.490 --> 00:25:52.380 align:middle line:90%
body.

