00:26:51.330 --> 00:26:55.530 align:middle line:84%
and remembering this
is where I want to go.

00:26:55.530 --> 00:26:58.450 align:middle line:84%
This is what's
actually within me.

00:26:58.450 --> 00:27:01.450 align:middle line:84%
It's not something
